            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E9%BC%BB%E7%82%8E%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%B8%E5%B9%B4%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%A3%E8%8A%82%E6%80%A7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E9%BC%BB%E7%82%8E%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%B8%E5%B9%B4%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%A3%E8%8A%82%E6%80%A7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#过敏性鼻炎分为常年性和季节性#</span></a>】医生介绍，过敏性鼻炎近年来患病率显著增加，主要症状是阵发性喷嚏、清水样涕、鼻痒、鼻塞，部分患者伴有眼痒、流泪、眼红等。常年性过敏性鼻炎过敏原多为尘螨、蟑螂、动物皮毛等；季节性过敏性鼻炎过敏原多为植物类花粉。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E9%BC%BB%E7%82%8E%E4%B8%8E%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E9%BC%BB%E7%82%8E%E4%B8%8E%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何区分过敏性鼻炎与感冒#</span></a>？👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4879112171618320" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hbz3l3urgwj60s00fr7bm02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/cOXLqN4Dlx083R6HUJhu01041200D3ny0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678798605&amp;ssig=GreIFgMeMy&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/7xqbqAWUlx083R6HdJwk01041200jPNV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;E