            <description><![CDATA[【如何治疗肛周脓肿和肛萎？一定要手术吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[苦涩]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/7e/2021_bitter_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】一般情况下，肛周脓肿和肛瘘具备相同的发病机制，都是严重的混合型感染。这两种疾病的治疗方式也具有极大的相似性，均需要手术治疗。那么肛周脓肿和肛瘘应如何通过手术方式进行治疗呢？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （科普中国）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4876660865171503" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hbra0xhd8dj61hc0u00yy02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/HEPPTD0Flx083GjVdqCY01041201Myfu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678798658&amp;ssig=BhgivipDDN&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/PmfVlRYolx083GjU6u7m01041200NBqb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678798658&amp;ssig=%2B%2BOvSahaO%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/y6V679r2lx083GjTTLqw01041200tjHi0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1678798658&amp;ssig=7ypGZ2waru&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4876660865171503&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
